name: Joe Dean's Github
body:
### Welcome
This is my GitHub page were I publish a collection of my class materials that I use to help teach kids how to code.

* [Scratch](http://joedean.github.io/coderdojo-scratch/)
* [Minecraft with ComputerCraft](http://joedean.github.io/computercraft/)
* [littleBits](http://littlebits.cc/)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
